description: This file is a source code module for jQuery, specifically handling AJAX functionalities including request setup, response handling, data conversion, and AJAX method definitions.

methods.name: addToPrefiltersOrTransports
methods.description: Creates a function to add prefilters or transports based on dataType.

methods.name: inspectPrefiltersOrTransports
methods.description: Inspects and applies prefilters or transports to AJAX options.

methods.name: ajaxHandleResponses
methods.description: Processes AJAX responses based on content-type and expected dataType.

methods.name: ajaxConvert
methods.description: Converts AJAX response data to the expected dataType.
